Bauba Platinum, Chrometco May Move: South African Equity Market Preview

-- B y   S t e p h e n   G u n n i o n
-- 
2011-07-05T22:01:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-05/bauba-platinum-chrometco-may-move-south-african-equity-preview.html
The following stocks may rise or fall
in  South Africa  today. Symbols are in parentheses and prices are
from the last close.  The FTSE/JSE Africa All Share Index advanced for an eighth
day, adding 176.45, or 0.6 percent, to 32,254.24 in
Johannesburg.  Bauba Platinum Ltd. (BAU)  : The explorer of platinum
group metals said it raised 50 million rand ($7.4 million) to
fund exploration. The stock was unchanged at 2 rand.  Chrometco Ltd. (CMO)  : The chrome development company
holds a general meeting of shareholders. The shares were
unchanged at 30 cents.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Gunnion in Johannesburg at 
 sgunnion@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at 
 gserkin@bloomberg.net  